data.name: sqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [supplier] ([supplierID], [organization], [fuel_Type], [contact], [supply_Price_Per_Liter], [amount_Of_Order], [Date_Of_Next_Order]) VALUES (@supplierID, @organization, @fuel_Type, @contact, @supply_Price_Per_Liter, @amount_Of_Order, @Date_Of_Next_Order); SELECT supplierID, organization, fuel_Type, contact, supply_Price_Per_Liter, amount_Of_Order, Date_Of_Next_Order FROM supplier WHERE (supplierID = @supplierID)

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [supplier] SET [supplierID] = @supplierID, [organization] = @organization, [fuel_Type] = @fuel_Type, [contact] = @contact, [supply_Price_Per_Liter] = @supply_Price_Per_Liter, [amount_Of_Order] = @amount_Of_Order, [Date_Of_Next_Order] = @Date_Of_Next_Order WHERE (([supplierID] = @Original_supplierID) AND ([organization] = @Original_organization) AND ([fuel_Type] = @Original_fuel_Type) AND ((@IsNull_contact = 1 AND [contact] IS NULL) OR ([contact] = @Original_contact)) AND ((@IsNull_supply_Price_Per_Liter = 1 AND [supply_Price_Per_Liter] IS NULL) OR ([supply_Price_Per_Liter] = @Original_supply_Price_Per_Liter)) AND ((@IsNull_amount_Of_Order = 1 AND [amount_Of_Order] IS NULL) OR ([amount_Of_Order] = @Original_amount_Of_Order)) AND ([Date_Of_Next_Order] = @Original_Date_Of_Next_Order)); SELECT supplierID, organization, fuel_Type, contact, supply_Price_Per_Liter, amount_Of_Order, Date_Of_Next_Order FROM supplier WHERE (supplierID = @supplierID)

data.name: sqlDeleteCommand1.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [supplier] WHERE (([supplierID] = @Original_supplierID) AND ([organization] = @Original_organization) AND ([fuel_Type] = @Original_fuel_Type) AND ((@IsNull_contact = 1 AND [contact] IS NULL) OR ([contact] = @Original_contact)) AND ((@IsNull_supply_Price_Per_Liter = 1 AND [supply_Price_Per_Liter] IS NULL) OR ([supply_Price_Per_Liter] = @Original_supply_Price_Per_Liter)) AND ((@IsNull_amount_Of_Order = 1 AND [amount_Of_Order] IS NULL) OR ([amount_Of_Order] = @Original_amount_Of_Order)) AND ([Date_Of_Next_Order] = @Original_Date_Of_Next_Order))
